{"tid":1292350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽繼續唱歌：唱歌是娛樂不是犯法","createTime":"2019-07-07T09:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T09:39:55.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5cecb05a23b59836b3cbcacbdb74b93c9677d4e0","tid":1292350,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:26:15.000Z","msg":"屯門公園大媽唱歌擾民且被指有傷風化，逾萬名市民昨日發起「光復屯門公園」行動，要求還屯門公園一個清靜。遊行過後，屯門公園今日有大媽重新開檔唱歌，吸引很多長者觀看，有大媽雖揚言只求大家開心，不一定有打賞，但仍然有長者打賞，大媽也伸手接利是。<br />\n<br />\n逾萬名市民遊行過後，屯門公園大媽今天明顯減少，現場目擊所見仍然有8至9檔大媽重新「開業」，一邊唱歌一邊跳舞，吸引大量長者在場圍觀。不過，當大媽的音量過大時，公園巡邏的保安會開喇叭提醒聲量過大，要求大媽將音量減低。<br />\n<br />\n有大媽高歌一曲後，向現場圍觀的阿伯強調只求大家開心，不要求一定有打賞，多謝大家的心意。不過，TOPick記者在現場所見，依然<span style=\"color: red;\">有阿伯打賞大媽，大媽也不拒絕伸手照收</span>。<br />\n<br />\n其中有一名阿伯手持紅色膠袋，他上前與大媽扭腰跳舞後，<span style=\"color: red;\">從一個紅色膠袋中拿出紙幣遞給大媽，大媽也以9秒9速度收下</span>，阿伯其後再與另一位大媽轉圈共舞，並拿出錢打賞。<br />\n<br />\n其中一位大媽接受訪問時稱，屯門公園是公眾場地，與民居有一段距離，不認為唱歌表演是擾民。她又稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">自己在屯門公園歌舞是一種娛樂，不是做犯法的事</span>，對於阿伯打賞，只是對她們工作的尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我會繼續來屯門公園唱歌！</span><br />\n<br />\n育有一名兩歲女兒的屯門港媽黃小姐，今天帶女兒到屯門公園共融遊樂埸玩時，又見到阿伯打賞大媽，直斥不雅，擔心影響小朋友，每次都要兜路行，已減少去屯門公園玩樂，期望當局正視，還屯門居民一個清靜的公園。<br />\n<br />\n現埸有市民稱，昨天才游行，大媽今天還夠膽出來繼續唱歌，不滿康文署辦事不力。據現場圍觀的市民表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">康文署今天有派人來向大媽登記</span>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhAvUKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhAvUKo.jpg&h=c4ce55c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPGrs4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPGrs4t.jpg&h=210eabb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 大媽繼續唱歌。（TOPick記者攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wwnm1py.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwnm1py.jpg&h=4e516b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 大媽繼續收取阿伯打賞。（TOPick記者攝）<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2394206/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2394206%2F&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=9616ed73\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2394206/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161cfc861ffdf358ba6ad970c5b3101f5c1089b9","tid":1292350,"uid":190727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"阻你少少位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20UgQgK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20UgQgK.png&h=a2f6a0f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b738d583ce33c0053fe22f348b663d2c912ced8","tid":1292350,"uid":61372,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"預左啦其實 康文署繼續唔做野<br />\n咪再整多次光復lo"},{"pid":"3277ba786f4fc2ad1315fabcef477d09b4d7c59e","tid":1292350,"uid":37869,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:28:05.000Z","msg":"行乞係犯法<br />\n表演跪地收錢就唔犯法？"},{"pid":"137581fbfb9f4c99482108e69430ac6ebd47c4ed","tid":1292350,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b738d583ce33c0053fe22f348b663d2c912ced8","tid":1292350,"uid":61372,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:27:54.000Z","msg":"預左啦其實 康文署繼續唔做野<br />\n咪再整多次光復lo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698e60b40e662e8bb0d7ebaaee07ec8403f1a398","tid":1292350,"uid":261430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T09:28:14.000Z","msg":"咁到底係娛樂定工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎左牌?"},{"pid":"b3c305a43271bfd33239547c4fbb5e91a60b2168","tid":1292350,"uid":68930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3277ba786f4fc